{"tid":838414,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多人唱淡IT","createTime":"2018-09-27T05:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T11:51:47.000Z","uid":155997,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2cb3104675096556c026e160d6135feb201caa","tid":838414,"uid":155997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"做左IT十幾廿年，由最初幫人切機、做technician、攪Network、跟住整網頁、寫Apps、到而家做Architect、跟Product。其實轉左咁多份工，從來都冇想過轉行。<br />\n做IT通常人工唔會好似D醫生、律師、飛機師咁高，仲會有時OT趕救火，但係整體都算舒舒服服、出份糧都夠養妻活兒，而且咁多年來IT都係好難請人，你正正常常基本一定搵到工。<br />\n所以當大家都自稱IT狗嘅時候，有冇諗過外行人只會越嚟越睇唔起我哋嘅專業，大家嘅人工同地位只會越嚟越低<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dac4cd53bbc00622463773249e49f5c5cd53c9a","tid":838414,"uid":23819,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"踩低啲咁咪少人入行 咁我地班老屎忽咪可以拓高啲個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4ede5ab55823b5c32cecf2fdbd198e6545eaec","tid":838414,"uid":184103,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"IT既技術唔係靠學習就得 多少睇天賦<br />\n有d無乜天賦既咪覺得IT難撈無人請"},{"pid":"f493ce71b6d01e14f1c06aab166ad28cbaa2ef10","tid":838414,"uid":76674,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"要不斷學新野已經夠你死"},{"pid":"2d3e125ac954c2e45c3f3e420227e11d09cf359d","tid":838414,"uid":10637,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f493ce71b6d01e14f1c06aab166ad28cbaa2ef10","tid":838414,"uid":76674,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"要不斷學新野已經夠你死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"你做任何既工你一世唔學新野未發唔到圍囉<br />\n<br />\n你好多工都係要定期增值自己啦"},{"pid":"fc54626387616cdc4b9975966ffb173918c4d62d","tid":838414,"uid":76674,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2d3e125ac954c2e45c3f3e420227e11d09cf359d","tid":838414,"uid":10637,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"